  "description": "<p><strong>🌟 About the Role</strong><br />This role involves <strong>face-to-face sales and marketing</strong>, where you’ll engage with the public and represent campaigns in a professional and ethical manner. You’ll communicate key messages clearly, build rapport, and contribute to campaign performance through direct outreach.</p><p>No prior experience is required. <strong>Full training and guidance will be provided</strong>. This role is suitable for individuals who are coachable, self-motivated, and open to working in a performance-based environment.</p><p><strong>Responsibilities</strong></p><ul><li>Engage the public through face-to-face marketing</li><li>Represent campaigns professionally</li><li>Communicate campaign messages clearly</li><li>Work with the team to achieve targets</li></ul><p><strong>What You’ll Gain</strong></p><ul><li>Structured sales & marketing training</li><li>Mentorship and ongoing support</li><li>Performance-based income and incentives</li><li>Personal growth in communication and confidence</li></ul>",
